  "instructions": [
    "Heat the oil in a large Dutch oven over medium heat.",
    "Add the onion, garlic, and ginger, and cook until the onion is translucent.",
    "Add the smoked turkey neck and cook until browned on all sides.",
    "Add the dried apricots, prunes, cinnamon, cumin, and paprika.",
    "Pour in the honey and apple cider vinegar, and stir to coat.",
    "Bring the mixture to a boil, then cover and transfer to the oven.",
    "Bake at 300°F (150°C) for 2 hours, or until the meat is tender and the sauce has thickened.",
    "Remove from the oven and let cool slightly before serving."
